14
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,479
No!

15
00:02:13,919 --> 00:02:15,000
Fine. Never mind then.

16
00:02:47,919 --> 00:02:49,000
Hello.

17
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:51,120
- Where's your boss? - Our boss is inside.

18
00:02:56,919 --> 00:02:58,039
Monkey, you are just in time...

19
