25
00:03:10,039 --> 00:03:12,120
With my creativity, the egg is worth 3.5 yuan each.

26
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:14,280
Altogether, I lost at least three yuan.

27
00:03:19,199 --> 00:03:20,199
What happened to you?

28
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:22,080
What's wrong with your waist?

29
00:03:24,439 --> 00:03:25,759
