35
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:40,280
Your girlfriend is getting married, but you are not the groom?

36
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,199
Are you serious?

37
00:03:45,319 --> 00:03:47,000
I think if I've been cheated on.

38
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:49,000
That doesn't matter at all, Monkey.

39
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,960
You know what? It's a good thing.

40
00:03:51,199 --> 00:03:53,759
First of all, I never liked that girl in the first place.

41
00:03:53,759 --> 00:03:55,240
