42
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,439
She's not interesting at all.

43
00:03:56,439 --> 00:03:58,520
You can easily find someone like her on the street.

44
00:03:58,840 --> 00:04:01,599
I'll introduce you to a good girl who can take care of the house...

45
00:04:01,599 --> 00:04:02,800
and who is hardworking, okay?

46
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:04,360
No, I was pathetic.

47
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:05,680
I was disgusting.

48
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:07,879
I treated her with all my heart and soul.

49
00:04:07,879 --> 00:04:10,080
I only cared about her.

50
00:04:10,439 --> 00:04:11,479
I did this and that.

51
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:13,159
Those episodes just popped out all of a sudden.

52
00:04:13,879 --> 00:04:14,919
Well...

53
00:04:15,759 --> 00:04:16,759
Go and find out...

54
00:04:17,050 --> 00:04:18,050
