55
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,439
Fine, I'll do it for you.

56
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:22,839
Can I ask a question?

57
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,639
Who caused the injury to your waist?

58
00:04:25,959 --> 00:04:27,050
You dropped your egg.

59
00:04:27,050 --> 00:04:28,399
Is that delicious, Tian Tian?

60
00:04:28,399 --> 00:04:29,879
