64
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:36,120
Here, Hai Xing Fried Rice version 2.0.

65
00:04:36,279 --> 00:04:37,800
The smiley face made just for you.

66
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:39,000
I can't stand that smiley face!

67
00:04:44,730 --> 00:04:45,730
Zhu Da Peng.

68
00:04:47,079 --> 00:04:48,730
Didn't you say you broke up with her?

69
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,170
Why is she so angry?

70
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:53,199
I don't know.

71
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:54,480
I'm telling you.

72
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:56,959
I, Li Xue Mei, am a decent lady.

73
00:04:57,639 --> 00:04:58,759
Don't think that...

74
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:00,360
